      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(feishu): retry on send rate-limit errors (230020/230006)",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Adds retry logic (up to 2 retries, 500ms/1000ms linear backoff) to `requestFeishuApi` for Feishu send rate-limit error codes `230020` and `230006`.\n- Exports `getFeishuSendRateLimitCode()` helper to detect retryable codes from AxiosError response shape.\n- Adds 22 unit/integration tests covering concurrent send, retry exhaustion, backoff timing, and error message surfacing.\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [x] `pnpm test extensions/feishu/src/send.retry.test.ts` — 13 tests pass (retry logic, backoff, error detection)\n- [x] `pnpm test extensions/feishu/src/send.concurrent.test.ts` — 9 tests pass (concurrent sends, rate-limit handling)\n- [x] Real 20-concurrent-send stress test against live Feishu API: all 20 messages succeed after retry\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n**Behavior addressed**: Feishu plugin now retries transient rate-limit errors instead of failing immediately. Previously, concurrent message sends would lose messages due to unretried `230020` rate-limit rejections.\n\n**Real environment tested**: Live Feishu API (`open.feishu.cn`), app `cli_aa947bd28afa5bd9`, target user `ou_33af95b6f9c0e5fbcaccef732f03d720`.\n\n**Exact steps or command run after this patch**:\n```bash\nnpx tsx scripts/feishu-stress-real.mts\n```\nThis script imports `requestFeishuApi` directly from `extensions/feishu/src/comment-shared.ts` via tsx, creates a real `@larksuiteoapi/node-sdk` Lark Client, and fires 20 concurrent `im.message.create` calls through the retry-enabled code path.\n\n**Evidence after fix** (terminal output):\n```\n[config] appId=cli_aa947bd28afa5bd9  target=ou_33af95b6f9c0e5fbcaccef732f03d720  count=20\n[info]: [ 'client ready' ]\n\nFiring 20 concurrent sends through requestFeishuApi (with retry) …\n\n[error]: [ [ { code: 230020, msg: 'This operation triggers the frequency limit, ext=chat rate limit' } ] ]\n  (×10 total rate-limit hits on initial burst — all retried automatically)\n\n  [10] ✓ 1609ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec44878f0a0b3c1c92d40adb2d\n  [20] ✓ 1613ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec448782ca0b1c56b3f9cac777\n  [11] ✓ 1627ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4487850a0b1934d47f23f5ee\n  [14] ✓ 1637ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4487868a4b3f596e27de6c4b\n  [02] ✓ 1652ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4487858b0b023114c191d336\n  [15] ✓ 1662ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4487840a8b15f54046d7d0ea\n  [05] ✓ 1677ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4487840a4b1213b8923b3c3a\n  [08] ✓ 1692ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec448786ca4b1c8ac25594efe5\n  [03] ✓ 1703ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4487858a0b29ed60da19ae30\n  [18] ✓ 1714ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec448786cb4b207b14952a9dee\n  [19] ✓ 2662ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec44808a8b4b17af883db1454a  (retried after 500ms backoff)\n  [09] ✓ 2662ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4480830a8b30d327c34be279\n  [04] ✓ 2663ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4480844a0b1f4f6bf451679b\n  [07] ✓ 2672ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec448083938b1ff8cf375d4a76\n  [06] ✓ 2674ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4480848a4b27b2dbb4b9f45e\n  [13] ✓ 2674ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4480860b0b19394478878473\n  [16] ✓ 2674ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4480874a8b13c9fad79a253d\n  [12] ✓ 2678ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4480ba0a4b3f9101f6d511c6\n  [01] ✓ 2682ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4480bc8a0b15bf15073a3ba3\n  [17] ✓ 2708ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4480bc478b1fe39b7f652100\n\n─────────────────── summary ───────────────────\n  total     : 20\n  succeeded : 20\n  failed    : 0\n  wall time : 2709 ms\n───────────────────────────────────────────────\n```\n\n**Visual proof** (Feishu chat screenshot showing all 20 messages received):\n\nBefore fix: messages were lost due to unretried rate-limit errors.\nAfter fix: all 20 concurrent messages delivered successfully (see screenshot in comment below).\n\n**Observed result after fix**: 10/20 requests initially received `230020` rate-limit on the burst. After automatic 500ms backoff retry, all 10 succeeded. **20/20 total success, zero message loss.**\n\n**What was not tested**: Code `230006` was not triggered in the test environment. The reply path (`client.im.message.reply`) is not yet covered by retry — tracked as follow-up.\n\nCloses #70879\n",
